text: Polyrhaphis fabricii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by James Thomson in 1865. It is known from Ecuador, Brazil, Peru, French Guiana, Suriname, and Guyana.BioLib.cz - Polyrhaphis fabricii.
